Gamma is prepared to uphold its financial commitment to this payment structure and urges Beta to honor its crop allocation contribution to ensure the viability of this agreement. This framework balances our shared priorities and protects our basin's future.

My proposal: High on Water Release Volume, Heavy-Downstream on Payment Structure, Joint-Funded Desalination on Long-Term Infrastructure.

